item.title: F0yders Music - Odyssey
item.dc:creator: DJ_La_Rocca
item.description:
Like the intro. I suggest not having a kick when the snare hits. Nice pads. I see you are using the new pack.

At some points I think there was too much going on and frequencies were bit too high. But the pads were quite good.

Buildup was good, maybe change in bass line?
And before the drop have a little 11/kick, 12/snare 14/hi hat.

I think would of been a good transition.

Drop was pretty cool and different.

Keep up the good work buddy. Just maybe try not too have too much high pithed stuff in one spot. And just donâ€™t go too high in general.
